data.system_settings: LG Fortune, Android 6.0.1, Windows 10 Pro, x64 (v1803)
data.actual_result: Android has a lightly shaded icon, while Desktop has a black icon (I figured this is an Android bug, since most mobile designs go off of Desktop version).
data.expected_result: They should both be the same.
data.short_description: In light theme, the members icon is very lightly shaded, instead of being black.
data.steps_to_repro: - On your Android device, notice the Member icon on Light theme. - Then, go to your desktop, notice the Member icon on Light theme as well.
